INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("370", "1", "2019-10-22 11:11:57", "2019-10-22 11:11:57", "<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>Welcome to hotel </h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://lotushotel.webhotel.vn/Content/images/es-hanoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lotus Hotel is located in the west of Hanoi. Lotus Hotel is a great destination and brings you the most enjoyable experience when you come to us. Come to Lotus Hotel, you will be immersed in fresh nature, to participate in leisure activities, relax to take away the sorrows and chaos of life. Lotus Hotel with all kinds of amenities and modern bungalows combined traditional style, restaurant system, conference room,  ...<br><br>Lotus Hotel with fully furnished rooms and villas, interior space is decorated in luxurious style mixed with traditional Vietnamese and modern Western. We have well trained, professional and professional staff, dedicated service.<br><br>Lotus Hotel offers a full range of amenities, fast check-in procedures, free public wi-fi coverage throughout the resort. The highlight of Lotus Hotel is the restaurant that offers both Western and Oriental cuisine built and served on the top floor. You can enjoy a delicious dinner while watching the starry sky and sea at night. In addition, guests can enjoy other services such as spa, gym in the resort area. It\'s great that your well-being, self-care habits are maintained on a regular basis.<br><br>Lotus Hotel is confident to bring you the emotional excitement, the best experience, the best in your stay. Come to us, we guarantee that you will not regret.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://lotushotel.webhotel.vn/Content/images/es-palace.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://lotushotel.webhotel.vn/Content/i