e, thanks to the dedication of the community, especially Github.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://st.quantrimang.com/photos/image/2017/03/10/Javascript.jpg\" alt=\"Kết quả hình ảnh cho javascript là gì\" /></figure>", "JavaScrip", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "javascrip", "", "", "2019-11-01 01:09:38", "2019-11-01 01:09:38", "", "0", "http://localhost/softwarestorepnv/?p=385", "0", "post", "", "0");
